Author: AngeloLacrime
Text: My dom said he was going to make me a taco on a day I was fasting .. hoo boy I started panicking. Instead of a taco I had 1/4 of a quest bar which was 48 calories and I felt like shit the rest of the night for breaking my fast just so he'd stop worrying about me.   #justEDthings😍  🙄 Lol .. sorry you're feeling that way. Sweet of him though.
